Package LibrarySearchGUI

Class Summary
AddListener Listener responsible for attempting to create and add a reference to the system based on the information the user has typed into the text fields of the addWindow
AddResetListener Reset listener responsible for resetting the text fields in the addWindow so that user can try again
addWindow Class that creates and manages user interactions for a GUI window corresponding to the add window for the LibrarySearch Managing application
mainWindow Class that creates and manages user interactions for a GUI window corresponding to the main window for the LibrarySearch application (users will see this window first)
referenceBox Class responsible for creating, and managing user interactions for, a combo box that allows user to choose between book and journal as their reference type in the addWindow
SearchListener Listener responsible for attempting to search for references based on the information the user has typed into the text fields of the searchWindow, and display the results on the screen in the required box
SearchResetListener Reset listener responsible for resetting the text fields in the searchWindow so that user can try again
searchWindow Class that creates and manages user interactions for a GUI window corresponding to the search window for the LibrarySearch application
